extendedInfo.description: Do you think you have a great visual memory? Try our new app Guess The City!Guess The City is a game where you have to guess the cities that are showed in the images.How many cities do you think you can recognize?Guess The City will test your knowledge of famous landmarks around the world. Guess the name of the city where the landmark/skyline can be found. Guess the city correctly will open the next level.-No ads.-Free app.
